le=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Judge Liman stopped short of issuing a g=
ag order, but he did adopt a rule restricting any out-of-court statements t=
hat could taint the proceedings. He made clear he wasn=E2=80=99t thrilled a=
bout doing so, saying he
didn=E2=80=99t want the case =E2=80=9Cdevolving into litigation over commen=
